"text": "auth-service/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 src/\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 app.(ts|py)          entry: wires middleware chain\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 config/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 env.*            loads .env (PORT, DB_URL, REDIS_URL, ...)\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 db/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 mysql.*          connection pool\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 redis.*          redis client\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 migrations/      001_create_users.sql\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 middlewares/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 validate.*       body validation (signup/signin shapes)\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 auth.*           cookie -> session_id -> Redis lookup\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 rateLimit.*      token bucket\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 routes/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.routes.*    /signup /signin /logout /protected\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 controllers/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.controller.* req/res only, no logic\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 services/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 auth.service.*   argon2 hash/verify, business rules\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 session.service.* create/get/delete session in Redis\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 utils/\n\u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 errors.*         generic 401, error middleware\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 tests/\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.e2e.test.*      the 5 pass/fail checks\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .env                     never committed\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 docker-compose.yml       mysql + redis local\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 nginx.conf               reverse proxy (deploy only)", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "auth-service/\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 src/\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 app.(ts|py)          entry: wires middleware chain\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 config/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 env.*            loads .env (PORT, DB_URL, REDIS_URL, ...)\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 db/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 mysql.*          connection pool\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 redis.*          redis client\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 migrations/      001_create_users.sql\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 middlewares/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 validate.*       body validation (signup/signin shapes)\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 auth.*           cookie -> session_id -> Redis lookup\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 rateLimit.*      token bucket\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 routes/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.routes.*    /signup /signin /logout /protected\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 controllers/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.controller.* req/res only, no logic\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 services/\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 auth.service.*   argon2 hash/verify, business rules\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 session.service.* create/get/delete session in Redis\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 utils/\n\u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 errors.*         generic 401, error middleware\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 tests/\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 auth.e2e.test.*      the 5 pass/fail checks\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 .env                     never committed\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 docker-compose.yml       mysql + redis local\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 nginx.conf               reverse proxy (deploy only)", "lineHeight": 1.25, "baseline": 13}, {"id": "DPdRO9YrxPbCkhdVipy2e", "type": "rectangle", "x": 870.0, "y": 60.0, "width": 560, "height": 150, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1971c2", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 1929245187, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1725048951, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1784469935471, "link": nul